OL,6,FA man who killed his son's girlfriend
OL,7,Fin a fit of rage has been found guilty
OL,8,Fof murder.
OL,10,FRichard Jones denied murdering Sophie
OL,11,FEvans, but admitted manslaughter,
OL,12,Fsaying he 'snapped' when he suspected
OL,13,Fthe victim and her boyfriend, his son
OL,14,FJamie Davies, were trying to defraud
OL,15,Fhim.
OL,17,FAfter a two-week trial, a jury found
OL,18,Fthe 50-year-old of Y Rhoddfa, Burry
OL,19,FPort guilty of murder
