OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering son's
OL,4,Cgirlfriend
OL,6,FThe court heard Jones visited Ms
OL,7,FEvans' home in Bigyn Road, Llanelli,
OL,8,Fat 9.19am on 5 July, 2024.
OL,10,FHe was recorded on a doorbell camera
OL,11,Ftalking on the phone with Sophie
OL,12,Fbefore she opened the front door to him
OL,14,FHe was inside the house for just 40
OL,15,Fminutes before CCTV captured him
OL,16,Frunning back to his car, returning to
OL,17,Fthe house and then driving off.
OL,19,FIn the moments before, he had attacked
OL,20,FSophie and left her for dead in her
OL,21,Fkitchen.
