OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering son's
OL,4,Cgirlfriend
OL,6,FFollowing the incident, CCTV spotted
OL,7,FJones driving to Llanelli town centre
OL,8,Fwhere he went to a bank and a bakery
OL,9,Fbefore going home to Burry Port.
OL,11,FBy 10.35am he had left his home
OL,12,Faddress by car and drove to Pembrey
OL,13,FCountry Park.
OL,15,FJones had sent several text to his ex-
OL,16,Fpartner telling them he thought he had
OL,17,Fbeen "scammed" and that he "won't be
OL,18,Fabout."
OL,20,FHe had suspected Sophie and his son
OL,21,FJamie Davies of trying to defraud him.
