OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering son's
OL,4,Cgirlfriend
OL,6,FAt 5.27pm, police received a 999-call
OL,7,Freporting that Richard Jones had
OL,8,Fkilled Sophie Evans.
OL,10,FOfficers immediately attended her
OL,11,Faddress and forced entry through the
OL,12,Fback door.
OL,14,FSophie's body was discovered on the
OL,15,Fkitchen floor and was confirmed dead
OL,17,FFifteen minutes later, Jones texted
OL,18,Fhis ex-partner asking her not to say
OL,19,Fanything.
