OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering son's
OL,4,Cgirlfriend
OL,6,FFollowing police enquiries, Jones was
OL,7,Ffound by officers near the entrance to
OL,8,FPembrey Country Park at 8pm.
OL,10,FHe was arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,11,Fand taken to hospital where he
OL,12,Fremained for four days.
OL,14,FWhen he arrived in custody on 9 July,
OL,15,F2024, Jones made a phone call to his
OL,16,Fmother in which he told her he had
OL,17,F"messed up again."
