OL,6,FOfficers found handwritten notes by
OL,7,FJones saying, "I got scammed and
OL,8,Frinsed by my own son, so I dealt with
OL,9,Fit myself, I had no other choice."
OL,11,FOn 11 July, he was charged with the
OL,12,Fmurder of Sophie Evans.
OL,14,FDetective Superintendent Gareth
OL,15,FRoberts said: "The guilty verdict of
OL,16,Fthe court is welcomed. Our thoughts at
OL,17,Fthis time are with Sophie and the
OL,18,Ffamily and friends who loved her.
