OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering son's
OL,4,Cgirlfriend
OL,6,F"Sophie was a young mother, beloved
OL,7,Ffamily member and friend. Richard
OL,8,FJones has been found guilty of what
OL,9,Fwas a senseless, cowardly act
OL,10,Ftriggered by anger and temper.
OL,12,F"Sophie was within her own home and
OL,13,Fnot in a position to defend herself
OL,14,Ffrom Richard Jones' cruel act of
OL,15,Fviolence. The family will take some
OL,16,Fcomfort that he's now removed from
OL,17,Fsociety and cannot harm any others."
OL,19,FJones will appear at court on 3 March
OL,20,Ffor sentencing.
